items.name: Salad
items.description: Lovely noodle salad with fresh veggies all tossed together for your liking.

items.name: Nacho's
items.description: A tortilla chip topped with melted cheese and hot pepper or refried beans.

items.name: Shrimp Carbonnara
items.description: An Italian pasta dish from Rome made with eggs,hard cheese,shrimp and black pepper.

items.name: Vegan Burger
items.description: This veggie burger has an amazing meaty texture and savory,smoky flavour,fit in a bun with fancy fixings or with good old ketchup and mustard.

items.name: Waffle
items.description: Delicious waffles topped with yummy,sticky syrup and ice-cream.

items.name: Milk Tart
items.description: Traditional South African milk tart with a homemade crust, and a silky smooth filling, baked to perfection and sprinkled with ground cinnamon.

items.name: French Chips (Small)
items.description: Fried sliced potatoes with seasoning and sauce of your desire.

items.name: Samoosa (5)
items.description: Baked pastry with a savory filling.

items.name: Soju 500ml
items.description: Traditional korean beer made from rice.

items.name: Milkshake
items.description: Sweet beverage made by blending milk, ice cream, and flavorings or sweeteners such as butterscotch, caramel sauce, chocolate syrup, fruit syrup, or whole fruit into a thick, sweet, cold mixture.

items.name: Deep-Fried Guacamole
items.description: Corn chip coated guac bites served with squeezed lime.

items.name: Pajeon (4)
items.description: Pan-fried korean scallion pancakes.

items.name: Paneer Pakora
items.description: Delicious Indian snack made with paneer, spice and gram flour.

items.name: Bruschetta (3)
items.description: Toasted bread, topped with tomatoes, parmesan cheese, garlic, and fresh basil.

items.name: Mince Vetkoek (3)
items.description: A delicious beef mince curry served with the good old South African favourite – Magwinya - a bread dough shaped into balls and deep-fried to perfection.

items.name: Spinach Enchilada
items.description: These Spinach Enchiladas are covered in a red enchilada sauce and stuffed with spinach, mushrooms and onions for a tasty Mexican dish.

items.name: Dol Sot Bi Bim Bap
items.description: Bibimbap (비빔밥) is Korean mixed rice. It includes rice, your choice of Korean side dishes and the bibimbap sauce. Served in a (mixing) bowl or in a hot stone bowl. Mix them all together nicely and shove them into your mouth

items.name: Butter Chicken
items.description: Aromatic golden chicken pieces in an incredible creamy curry sauce.

items.name: Lemon Chicken Piccata
items.description: Tender breaded chicken in a creamy lemon sauce that the entire family will love!

items.name: Potjiekos
items.description: South African lamb stew made on the flames to keep you warm.

items.name: Dulce De Leche
items.description: Confection of sweet milk cooked down until it's the color and consistency of caramel sauce or butterscotch

items.name: Bungeoppang
items.description: Bungeo means crucian carp and Ppang means bread in Korean, so the dessert is simply named after what it is and looks like,filled with chocolate and ice-cream.

items.name: Kheer
items.description: This traditional Indian rice pudding made with basmati rice, whole milk, sugar, nuts, saffron and cardamom is slow-cooked to perfection making for a rich, creamy kheer.

items.name: Tiramisu Cheesecake
items.description: Yummy! creamy cheesecake, a slice of happiness.

items.name: Malva Pudding
items.description: Sweet and moist cake recipe straight from South Africa made with incredible apricot jam and heavy custard.

items.name: Apple Pie
items.description: Perfectly cooked (not mushy) apples surrounded by a thickened and gently spiced sauce all baked inside a flaky, golden-brown crust.
